54:49.536 --> 54:51.151
Farewell, my concubine.

54:51.330 --> 54:54.288
-And I'll take a Bud. Thanks for asking.
-And an Old Grand-Dad.

54:54.458 --> 54:57.165
The bourbon. Not some old guy.

54:59.171 --> 55:00.502
Words With Friends?

55:00.672 --> 55:03.334
Some people just call it texting.

55:04.176 --> 55:08.294
I wanna ask you about the night
Susan Knight died.

55:09.264 --> 55:12.176
Heh. Of course you do. It's a party.

55:12.684 --> 55:16.893
The memorial video got me thinking.
I've never really heard what happened.

55:17.606 --> 55:18.641
[SIGHS]

55:18.816 --> 55:22.604
