on a boat after about 15 minutes

55:30.494 --> 55:34.612
Woke up the next morning and everyone
is freaking out because they can't find Susan.

55:34.790 --> 55:37.873
Ripped the boat apart looking for her...

55:38.043 --> 55:39.999
